</div>

<style>
  /* The bottom padding is not whitespace — it is clearance. `.hero::after` is
     the paper curve, and it rises ~85px above the hero's own bottom edge. The
     index has to end above that line or the curve eats the last three labels. */
  /* WHO I AM — the About section. Two columns: the narrative on the left, a
     scannable strengths list on the right, so a fast reader gets the capability
     list and a slow one gets the story. Paper, flowing out of the hero's curve. */
